'''Lewis MacLeod''' is a Scottish actor. In the realm of voice acting, he is best known as [[wikipedia:Sebulba|Sebulba]] in ''[[wikipedia:Star Wars Episode I: The Phantom Menace|The Phantom Menace]]'' and [[wikipedia:Postman Pat|Postman Pat]] in the eponymous show.

==Roles==
* [[2006]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II]]'': Hadhod, Dwarf Sage, Additional voices
* [[2004]]: ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Third Age]]'': Hadhod, [[Sharku]]
